DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Recreation-Ge
 neral\\nJoin the Swarthmore Philadelphia Connections Committee for a meani
 ngful morning of history\, community\, and service as we celebrate Earth D
 ay. Experience Fair Hill’s dedication to community revitalization and en
 vironmental stewardship. We invite you to volunteer with fellow Swatties d
 uring a beautiful spring day at this historic site. Program10 a.m. | Tour 
 of historic Fair Hill Burial Ground with Executive Director Kerry Roeder11
  a.m. | Join a Volunteer Service Project RSVP We look forward to seeing yo
 u there!\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3
 Devent%26eventid%3D1376575573
