SUMMARY:History Dept. End-of-Semester Gathering: Critical Karaoke
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['History']\\nCategory: Meeting\\nWhat is Critica
 l Karaoke? It's not singing (unless you're so moved)! As recently done by
  French historians at a few conferences\, Critical Karaoke invites scholar
 s to choose a song (or other short musical excerpt in any genre) and prese
 nt on its relationship to their own research (which need not be music-rela
 ted). \\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3D
 event%26eventid%3D1388710002
