SUMMARY:CAIC Listening Session: Faculty
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Office of Diversity'\, 'Equity'\, 'and Inclusi'
 ]\\nCategory: Meeting\\nVice President for Diversity\, Equity\, and Inclus
 ion Brooke Vick recently shared the results of Swarthmore’s Campus Cultu
 re & Climate Survey with our community. The survey captured student\, facu
 lty\, and staff perspectives on living\, learning and working at Swarthmor
 e — you can learn more and find the full report on the Campus Climate S
 urvey website.   What do faculty members think about the survey findings?
  Do they reflect your experience at the College? What would you like to se
 e come out of this survey\, as we plan together for the future of Swarthmo
 re?   Faculty are invited to join members of the Committee on Access\, In
 clusion\, and Community (CAIC) to share your thoughts on survey findings\,
  and what could come next.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?
 trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1390294611
LOCATION:McCabe LibLab\, Full Space\, Conference Room
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1390294611
CATEGORIES:Meeting
