SUMMARY:Senior Honors Thesis Staged Reading
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Theater']\\nCategory: Performance\\nSpring 2026
  Honors Playwriting Thesis  The Night of Ended Secrets by Frank Paz (‘2
 6) Directed by Andrew Watring Jamie and Carmine\, two estranged childhood 
 friends\, reconnect as they sit vigil for the death of Jamie’s grandmoth
 er. As Jamie struggles to write his eulogy\, he must choose: keep a secret
  out of love for his grandmother or risk living his authentic truth. Writt
 en by Frank Paz (‘26)\, The Night of Ended Secrets pits familial obliga
 tion against burning desire against the setting of one family’s grief. 
   Performance at 8:00 p.m. Martin Hall 028 - Ping and Rose Chen Screening
  Room    \\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=vie
 w%3Devent%26eventid%3D1389654288
LOCATION:Martin Hall 028 Ping and Rose Chen Screening Room
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1389654288
CATEGORIES:Performance
