SUMMARY:SwatWalks: Oakland
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Reception\\nS
 tep outside and connect with your local community through SwatWalks\, our 
 new alumni-led series of outdoor social strolls! We are kicking off our ve
 ry first outing in the Bay Area with a walk around Oakland's Lake Merritt
 . Join host Margaret Huang '87 and fellow alumni for our inaugural SwatWal
 ks: Oakland — a casual\, family-friendly walk around scenic Lake Merritt
 \, the nation's first wildlife refuge. Join this easy 3-mile walk\, which 
 is perfect for all ages and abilities. Whether you’re seeking fresh air\
 , lively conversation\, or just a great reason to get outside\, this is yo
 ur morning. Afterward\, join us for an optional brunch and music at Lake C
 halet. Bring your sunscreen and your Swat spirit — let's walk\, talk\, a
 nd enjoy the spring. Lake Chalet1520 Lakeside DrOakland\, CA 94612 Sign up
 \, RSVP here!\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=v
 iew%3Devent%26eventid%3D1385106148
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1385106148
CATEGORIES:Reception
END:VEVENT
