SUMMARY:Breakfast Cooking Class
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Dining Services']\\nCategory: Training/Workshop
 \\nJoin The Swarthmore Chef team for a fun\, fast-paced cooking class that
  teaches the essential skills every beginner needs. In just one hour\, par
 ticipants will learn how to cook perfect eggs\, make quick and tasty micro
 wave meals\, and build confidence with basic kitchen techniques. The class
  is upbeat\, hands-on\, and designed to show that great cooking doesn’t 
 require fancy tools. Students will pick up practical tips they can use imm
 ediately in their daily routines.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmor
 e.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1389756403
