SUMMARY:Campus Culture & Climate Survey Report Listening Sessions: Staff
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Office of Diversity'\, 'Equity'\, 'and Inclusi'
 ]\\nCategory: Meeting\\nVice President for Diversity\, Equity\, and Inclus
 ion Brooke Vick recently shared the results of Swarthmore’s Campus Cul
 ture & Climate Survey with our community. The survey captured student\
 , faculty\, and staff perspectives on living\, learning and working at Swa
 rthmore — you can learn more and find the full report on the Campus Cl
 imate Survey website.What do you think about the survey findings? Do th
 ey reflect your experience at the College? What would you like to see com
 e out of this survey\, as we plan together for the future of Swarthmore?M
 eals for ALL in-person sessions are covered by the Office of DEI.If you ca
 n’t make these sessions\, you can attend another one of the sessions li
 sted on the Events page of the Campus Climate Survey website (please
  log in with your Swarthmore credentials to view)\, share your input throu
 gh our feedback form\, or email culturesurvey@swarthmore.edu. We look fo
 rward to hearing from you!\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?
 trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1390047766
LOCATION:Dining Center 150 - Elizabeth Economy '84 and David Michael Wah Di
 ning Room
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1390047766
CATEGORIES:Meeting
END:VEVENT
